articles.title: Hagedorn helps South Dakota slip past Denver 80-78
articles.description: VERMILLION, S.D. (AP) — Tyler Hagedorn totaled 26 points, six rebounds, five assists and two blocks and South Dakota outlasted Denver 80-78 on Sunday.
articles.content:
VERMILLION, S.D. (AP) Tyler Hagedorn totaled 26 points, six rebounds, five assists and two blocks and South Dakota outlasted Denver 80-78 on Sunday.
